{"tid":2336824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：黑客攻擊或涉中國； 拜登︰請認清俄羅斯黑客的所為","createTime":"2020-12-23T01:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T03:44:38.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7b1ceb5ff5b10e1597f4592d6013a7b7e979e2","tid":2336824,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"拜登︰黑客攻擊未受控 上任後將再推刺激經濟方案<br />\n<br />\n美國政府多個部門早前受黑客攻擊，候任總統拜登質疑情況仍未受控，形容是重大和持續的風險。拜登批評總統特朗普未有做好防禦工作，促請特朗普認清俄羅斯黑客的所為，又指華府部門在好多事情上沒有向他匯報，他看不到任何跡象顯示事件已經受控，會在上任後會加強網絡安全工作。拜登又說國會昨日通過的9000億美元刺激經濟方案，雖不算完美，但可解燃眉之急，他預告上任後會再推出新一輪刺激經濟方案，會集中應對失業、支援小企業和疫苗分發工作。<br />\n<br />\n拜登又說，對日前接種的新型冠狀病毒疫苗充滿信心，期待接種第二劑，但疫苗分發需時，呼籲民眾繼續保持社交距離和戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2371856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2371856&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=a2f9f853\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2371856</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"medium\">特朗普首度回應黑客攻擊多個政府部門 被指淡化俄羅斯角色 矛頭轉向中國<br />\n2020/12/20 &mdash; 8:51<br />\n節錄<br />\n美國總統特朗普首次回應政府部門電腦系統遭黑客入侵事件，被質疑刻意淡化俄羅斯黑客的角色，反而把矛頭指向中國。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在 Twitter 指，是「報道假新聞的傳媒」誇大黑客入侵事件，稱情況已受控，又指媒體事事都針對俄羅斯，卻因為利益關係，不敢提到可能涉事的中國。他接著又指黑客可能都有入侵選舉系統，再次大罵選舉腐敗舞弊。不過，他並無提出任何中國同是次黑客攻擊有關的證據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普首度回應黑客攻擊多個政府部門-被指淡化俄羅斯角色-矛頭轉向中國\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2-%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B&d=OIqfWdBnlTXAQE%2BUUTKEpBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=3a445e41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E9%A6%96%E5%BA%A6%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E6%B7%A1%E5%8C%96%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%A7%92%E8%89%B2-%E7%9F%9B%E9%A0%AD%E8%BD%89%E5%90%91%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B&h=5c3ad9ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普首度回應黑客攻擊多個政府部門-被指淡化俄羅斯角色-矛頭轉向中國</a></span>"},{"pid":"25dd8cda8534e2c7faa08995ffb2ecac06424286","tid":2336824,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"立場真係好憎侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d10e83588d5534c0430bc290ba64459cc4ac5c7","tid":2336824,"uid":377617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"拜登︰唔好激嬲中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請大家打返稻草人!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"d67f9079b60b0a28dff2bc791f1347545bc0e1c9","tid":2336824,"uid":14718,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"25dd8cda8534e2c7faa08995ffb2ecac06424286","tid":2336824,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:23:45.000Z","msg":"立場真係好憎侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:25:05.000Z","msg":"有名俾你叫垃場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d8ff70c378f573f3ed31ff1debf368a9a5e359","tid":2336824,"uid":24168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"究竟sleepy joe 係點樣響冇接觸國家安全情報之下，確認係俄仔所為？"},{"pid":"61c52cc2601bf2bffbbf67ad6a4b08e16de0af0f","tid":2336824,"uid":76310,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"59d8ff70c378f573f3ed31ff1debf368a9a5e359","tid":2336824,"uid":24168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"究竟sleepy joe